
# colonizer
{{ npm.link("colonizer") }} is a small `JavaScript/TypeScript` library for handling colonArgs.

I felt the need for `colonizer` when I was working on {{ gh.link("iaseth/josn") }}.

I am using {{ gh.link("iaseth/readmix", "readmix") }} for generating this README.
You can view the source file [here](https://github.com/iaseth/colonizer/blob/master/README.md.rx).


